abstract: Governments reports will include sales of new homes for April, and companies reporting earnings will include Campbell Soup, Home Depot, Hewlett-Packard and SABMiller.
snippet: Governments reports will include sales of new homes for April, and companies reporting earnings will include Campbell Soup, Home Depot, Hewlett-Packard and SABMiller.
lead_paragraph: ECONOMIC REPORTS Data will include sales of existing homes for April (Wednesday); weekly jobless claims and sales of new homes for April (Thursday); and durable goods orders for April (Friday).

headline.main: Economic Reports for the Week Ahead
